## Additional Terms for EPLQ Project

This software implements privacy-preserving location-based query systems. 
Users and developers should be aware of the following:

### Privacy Notice
- This software processes location data using encryption
- No unencrypted location data should be stored or transmitted
- Users have the right to export and delete their data
- Compliance with GDPR, CCPA, and other privacy regulations is recommended

### Security Considerations
- Regular security audits are recommended
- Keep dependencies updated for security patches
- Use secure configuration in production environments
- Monitor for security vulnerabilities and apply patches promptly

### Research and Academic Use
- This software is suitable for research and academic purposes
- Citations to the EPLQ project are appreciated in academic work
- Commercial use is permitted under the MIT License terms
- Contributions back to the open source project are encouraged

### Disclaimer
- This software is provided for educational and research purposes
- Users are responsible for compliance with applicable laws and regulations
- The authors are not liable for any misuse or damages resulting from use
- Security features should be thoroughly tested before production deployment